<div id="review_732187794" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/732187794" />
    <a title="Alexander Nelson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/24388967-alexander-nelson"><img alt="Alexander Nelson" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/732187794?book_show_action=true">Oct 01, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alexander Nelson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alexander Nelson" href="/user/show/24388967-alexander-nelson">Alexander Nelson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer732187794" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer831161571216349599">This is a wonderful and moving book, and hard to put down. Peppe writes what could be dark or distressing scenes that are instead instilled with a self-depreciating hilarity that pulls you in and pulls you along. The whole story is so three dimensional that you really know the characters and can feel empathy for almost all of them, even when they are behaving in ways you can&apos;t understand. Highly recommended.</span>
  <span id="freeText831161571216349599" style="display:none">This is a wonderful and moving book, and hard to put down. Peppe writes what could be dark or distressing scenes that are instead instilled with a self-depreciating hilarity that pulls you in and pulls you along. The whole story is so three dimensional that you really know the characters and can feel empathy for almost all of them, even when they are behaving in ways you can't understand. Highly recommended.</span>
  <a data-text-id="831161571216349599" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review732187794">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
